reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nifty Android Tablet
reviews.reviewText: Well-designed, well-made functional tablet computer. LCD screen is a little slow to respond to touch until I added an SD card. Straightforward to set up. I did an over-the-air configuration with my Google account. My wife saw how well the little machine worked and decided it should be hers. It was easy to perform a factory reset. This time I used a cable and USB adapter and the included cable to transfer data from her phone to the tablet. The process took a while, but worked great. My wife’s Galaxy S7 Tab is starting to run slowly, and she plans to replace it with this.
